reut2-000.sgm, CENERGY &lt;CRG> REPORTS 4TH QTR NET PROFIT, Cenergy Corp reported fourth quarter netincome of 790,000 dlrs or seven cts per share on revenues of7.7 mln dlrs.    For the year it reported a net loss of 6.5 mln dlrs or 70cts per share as a result of writedowns in the book value ofits oil and gas properties in the first two quarters. Revenueswere 37 mln dlrs.    Following the company's fiscal year ended March 31, 1985,it changed to a calender year end.    For the nine months ended Dec 31, 1985, it reported a lossof 63.4 mln dlrs or 6.54 dlrs per share on revenues of 47.6 mlndlrs, which it said was a result of noncash writedowns of oiland gas properties.    For the year ended March 31, 1985, Cenergy reported netincome of 3,705,000 dlrs or 36 cts per share on revenues of 71mln dlrs.    The company said its reserves during the year fell to fivemln barrels from 6.4 mln barrels of oil and to 60.1 bilioncubic feet of gas from 63.7 BCF. It said these reserves did notdisappear but are available to produce as prices recover. Reuter&#3;
