reut2-000.sgm, NEITHER SIDE OPTIMISTIC ON ROTTERDAM PORT ISSUES, Employers and the port union, FNV, areto meet again this afternoon to attempt a settlement of thesix-week-old dispute in Rotterdam's general cargo sector, butneither side is optimistic, spokesmen for both sides toldReuters.    Little progress was made in last night's three hours oftalks, with both sides largely reiterating their positions.    There is still a very large gap between the employers andthe FNV

